snippet.title: Afterparty Update for Touhou Danmuki ~ Spellbroken Dream Festival is Available Now!
snippet.description:
東方弾夢記 v1.10a

A brand-new update to this Touhou-style fangame, adding a new playable character and new spells, all just as free as ever! Why not give it a try?

Download: https://insys.itch.io/sdf
Alternate download: https://www.bulletforge.org/u/arkeeneum/p/touhou-danmuki-spellbroken-dream-festival
Twitter release announcement: https://twitter.com/IncandescenceSy/status/1606325517191258117


Discord: Incandescence~ ♡#8301; Twitter: @IncandescenceSy
